@Demo_HostAddress = http://localhost:5277

### List products
GET {{Demo_HostAddress}}/api/products
Accept: application/json

###

### Get product
GET {{Demo_HostAddress}}/api/products/{{productId}}
Accept: application/json

@productId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

###

### Create product
POST {{Demo_HostAddress}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sample Product",
  "description": "Beginner CQRS demo item",
  "price": 19.99,
  "status": 1
}

###
